---
title: Ultimate Summer Salad with Crisp Radish, Sugar Snap Peas, and Fresh Mozzarella
description: What makes this salad ultimate? We’re not quite sure exactly. It’s so much more than the sum of its parts! Herby pesto and fresh mozzarella might be a big part of it.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ultimate-summer-salad-0060371c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/-2874b597.pdf
